{
  "stem": "2590.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I want it now.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You told me you'll give it to me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He said, you have no choice.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because if you'll talk too long, you'll be arrested.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And somehow, I was under the impression that somebody is watching us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And sure enough, if it was prearranged or not-- I think it was prearranged.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This Ukrainian policeman came to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he took me to the police.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he told something to the German authorities.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know what he told them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But the German took his rifle, he started to hit me in the face.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He knocked several teeth out, and my nose started to bleed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Blood was gushing from my nose and from my mouth.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I told him to kill me, but he said no.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You'll struggle a little longer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And until today, I don't remember how I got back into the ghetto and to the hospital.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the only thing they could do in the hospital is to put ice packs on my nose.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And my nose is crooked until today.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I had a few broken teeth loose and they pulled them out, extracted the teeth.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And for months, I looked like a misfit.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You know, a 16-year-old girl without front teeth, with a crooked, but nothing could be done.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And it was November already, and there were rumors that they're going to-- the people that do not have labor cards are going to be sent to a labor camp.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I didn't have any labor papers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So my sister and my mother said-- my sister had, and my mother-- that they'll go with me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But unfortunately, maybe fortunately, one person died in the hospital, and they gave me her labor card.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And it was-- that's the way I remained.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
